  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Infrared Diode Laser on Improvement of Scar and Prevention of Recurrence of Excised Keloid</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Infra-red Diode Laser on Improvement of Surgical Scar and on the Prevention of Excised Keloids Recurrence-Pilot Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
