  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years and older

          -  Skin type from I to VI (Fitzpatrick classification scale)

          -  Scar longer than 4cm for plastic surgery's patients OR scar longer than 2cm for keloid
             patients

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Malignant tumor pathology

          -  Infectious or viral skin disease

          -  Immunosuppressive pathology and/or immunosuppressive treatment,

          -  Long-term corticosteroid treatment

          -  Pregnant woman
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
